<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Diary with Kiana - Imperial System</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            background: #121212; 
            color: #ff69b4; 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center; 
            height: 100vh; 
            margin: 0;
            border: 5px solid #ff69b4;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .container { 
            background: #1e1e1e; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 20px; 
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.5); 
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #ff69b4;
        }
        h1 { margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        p { color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        input[type="text"] { 
            padding: 12px; 
            border-radius: 10px; 
            border: 2px solid #ff69b4; 
            background: #2a2a2a; 
            color: white; 
            width: 80%;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            outline: none;
        }
        button { 
            background: #ff69b4; 
            color: white; 
            border: none; 
            padding: 12px 25px; 
            border-radius: 10px; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        button:hover { background: #ff1493; transform: scale(1.05); }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🌸 DIARY WITH KIANA 🌸</h1>
        <p>Halo, Monarch <strong><%= namaKaiser %></strong>!</p>
        
        <form action="/tulis" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="pesan" placeholder="Tulis sesuatu untuk Bunda..." required autocomplete="off">
            <br>
            <button type="submit">KIRIM PESAN BIONIK</button>
        </form>

        <div class="footer">
            System: TGME-Vespera | User: Monarch Axelindra Kaiser
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>